hands_on_practices.solution:
我们用$J$表示循环通量，所以在长期平衡中，对于每种催化剂$A$，我们有
$$
J \;=\;\lambda_A\,n_A\,,\quad\forall A\in\{12,13,14,15\}\,.
$$
总催化剂丰度$N_C=n_{12}+n_{13}+n_{14}+n_{15}$守恒，于是给出
$$
N_C
=\sum_A n_A
=\sum_A\frac{J}{\lambda_A}
=J\sum_A\frac{1}{\lambda_A}
\quad\Longrightarrow\quad
J=\frac{N_C}{\displaystyle\sum_A\frac{1}{\lambda_A}}\,.
$$
在修正之前，我们有
$$
\lambda_{12}=k_{12}\lambda_{14},\quad
\lambda_{13}=k_{13}\lambda_{14},\quad
\lambda_{14}=\lambda_{14},\quad
\lambda_{15}=k_{15}\lambda_{14},
$$
因此
$$
\sum_A\frac{1}{\lambda_A}
=\frac{1}{k_{12}\lambda_{14}}
+\frac{1}{k_{13}\lambda_{14}}
+\frac{1}{\lambda_{14}}
+\frac{1}{k_{15}\lambda_{14}}
=\frac{1}{\lambda_{14}}\Bigl(\tfrac{1}{k_{12}}+\tfrac{1}{k_{13}}+1+\tfrac{1}{k_{15}}\Bigr).
$$
因此，原始的循环通量为
$$
J
=\frac{N_C}{\tfrac{1}{\lambda_{14}}\bigl(\tfrac{1}{k_{12}}+\tfrac{1}{k_{13}}+1+\tfrac{1}{k_{15}}\bigr)}
=\frac{N_C\,\lambda_{14}}{\displaystyle\Bigl(\tfrac{1}{k_{12}}+\tfrac{1}{k_{13}}+1+\tfrac{1}{k_{15}}\Bigr)}.
$$
修正之后，$\lambda'_{14}=\alpha\,\lambda_{14}$，而$\lambda'_{12}=\lambda_{12},\lambda'_{13}=\lambda_{13},\lambda'_{15}=\lambda_{15}$保持不变。因此
$$
\sum_A\frac{1}{\lambda'_A}
=\frac{1}{k_{12}\lambda_{14}}
+\frac{1}{k_{13}\lambda_{14}}
+\frac{1}{\alpha\lambda_{14}}
+\frac{1}{k_{15}\lambda_{14}}
=\frac{1}{\lambda_{14}}\Bigl(\tfrac{1}{k_{12}}+\tfrac{1}{k_{13}}+\tfrac{1}{\alpha}+\tfrac{1}{k_{15}}\Bigr),
$$
新的通量为
$$
J'
=\frac{N_C}{\tfrac{1}{\lambda_{14}}\bigl(\tfrac{1}{k_{12}}+\tfrac{1}{k_{13}}+\tfrac{1}{\alpha}+\tfrac{1}{k_{15}}\bigr)}
=\frac{N_C\,\lambda_{14}}{\displaystyle\Bigl(\tfrac{1}{k_{12}}+\tfrac{1}{k_{13}}+\tfrac{1}{\alpha}+\tfrac{1k_{15}}\Bigr)}.
$$
由于能量产生率$\epsilon_{CNO}\propto J$，新旧速率之比为
$$
\frac{\epsilon'_{CNO}}{\epsilon_{CNO}}
=\frac{J'}{J}
=\frac{
\bigl(\tfrac{1}{k_{12}}+\tfrac{1}{k_{13}}+1+\tfrac{1}{k_{15}}\bigr)
}{
\bigl(\tfrac{1}{k_{12}}+\tfrac{1}{k_{13}}+\tfrac{1}{\alpha}+\tfrac{1}{k_{15}}\bigr)
}\,.
$$
